# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Large binaries — exceed GitHub's 100 MB per-file limit.
#  The installer is distributed as a RELEASE ASSET, not committed.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.exe
*.zip
opencode-source.zip

# Compiled launcher (regenerated by the build)
launcher.exe

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  SECURITY — never commit credentials, sessions, or USB runtime data.
#  These can contain API keys and full AI conversation transcripts.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
data/xdg/
data/tmp/
data/config/node_modules/
sessions/
Sessions/
**/auth.json
**/opencode.db
**/opencode.db-*
diagnostic-report.txt

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  The payload — third-party binaries (OpenCode, Node.js, WezTerm).
#  Too large for git; fetched from official sources at build time.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Portable-OpenCode-USB-Backup/
bin/
nodejs/
wezterm/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Build / OS noise
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
create-usb.log
*.log
*.tmp
z*.tmp
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
System Volume Information/
